The code has a main function that contains very little code, and only refers to other functions to make it as easy to read as possible.

Code structure:

1) Declaration of libraries

2) the creation of global variables

3) void setup: adds the correct PIN and prepares everything, such as addressing

4) main loop: 4.1 creates communication, 4.2 gets commands, 4.3 drives to scanned QR code, 4.4 before turns to the right commands

5) Functions: 5.1 functions of turns -> swing, straight ahead, left, right.

6) functions: follower path, read QR code, Tick means that it counts on the wheel -> distance

7) Features: reads ToF sensors

8) Features: Bluetooth

9) Features: Swing conditions, with PWM

10) Features: reads light sensor and checks battery level
